            <ui:Label name="HelpPageDescription" text="Learn how to integrate and deploy games for hosting on GameLift. The GameLift service manages game server deployment, operation, and scaling.&#10;You can deploy custom-built game servers or use GameLift Realtime Servers to configure lightweight game servers for your game."/>
        </ui:VisualElement>
